snippet.title: Hatsune Miku:  Project DIVA - Hello, Planet Minigame
snippet.description:
From a DLC.
8-bit Miku. :3

That goddamn Sphinx. -_-  My lack of Japanese makes it even harder.
Thankfully, there's a "cheat sheet" out there. :3:
http://yue801.blog45.fc2.com/blog-entry-346.html

Ending 1 is with the standard ol' clear item.
Ending 2 is from getting all of the notes and watering the pot for some other clear item.  I found out late.  If I had known, I would've collected all the notes.

Sphinx section is abridged because I was using the "cheat sheet".
